try

    for (i = 3; i &gt;= 1; --i) {
         System.out.println(i);
    }

You should write you code like:

    public class ForLoops {
        public static void main (String [] args) {
      
           int firstNumber;
           int i;

           firstNumber = 3;

           for (i = firstNumber; i &gt;= 1; --i) {
              System.out.println(i);
           }
       }
    }

